Pluto is a Question and Answer (Q&A) forum whose design is inspired by StackOverflow_ 
and YahooAnswers_ and other similar projects (to lesser extent). 

Pluto is written in Python_ on top of Django_ platform and supports MySQL and PostgeSQL database backends.

If you have any questions installing or tweaking pluto - please do not hesitate to ask
at the forum_ or email to admin@pluto.org.

Online documentation is available at: http://pluto.org/doc/index.html

Also there is an offline copy of the documentation in pluto/doc/source

Code of Pluto grew out of CNPROG_ project originally written by 
`Mike Chen <http://cn.linkedin.com/in/mikegangchen>`_ and Sailing Cai.
